commentable_entity.description: Warner Bros is no court and Ted Turner is no judge, they have no right and no justification to try to ruin Johnny Depp's career based on biased allegations that are not of their competence.  We are outraged by  Warner Bros standing with the abusers. But we are giving you a chance to stop us from  boycotting your Studio and all your other projects from now by PUBLICLY APOLOGISING TO JOHNNY DEPP! We won't stand with you  if you stand with the abusers !

commentable_entity.petition_title: Warner Brothers Studios: Warner Bros must publicly apologise to Johnny Depp

comment: Warner Brothers, Ted Turner, Disney and its other affiliates chose to be judge, jury and executioner, shame on you all. What egos you must have to think because of your $$, you can do whatever you want. While that may be true to an extent, what you love most $, will be affected. Johnny Depp’s fans are loyal to the core, much more loyal than to your “films” or “companies”. Your bottom line will reflect your bad decision. Millions of Depp fans will boycott this franchise, fans who would have brought in millions of those beloved $$ you so desperately crave. I gave up Disney and it’s other companies long ago, but even I would have broken my rule to watch Johnny Depp in Fantastic Beasts 3. Your choice to remove Johnny Depp, just validated my choice! Thank you for reminding me why I no longer watch anything put out by Disney and it’s partners, and reinforcing that my choice was correct.

commentable_entity.title: Warner Brothers Studios: Warner Bros must publicly apologise to Johnny Depp
commentable_entity.description: Warner Bros is no court and Ted Turner is no judge, they have no right and no justification to try to ruin Johnny Depp's career based on biased allegations that are not of their competence.  We are outraged by  Warner Bros standing with the abusers. We will not watch Acquaman because Amber Heard is in it. And we will definitely NOT watch  Fantastic Beasts without Johnny Depp as Grindelwald. We aren't asking you to fix Fantastic Beasts or take Johnny Depp back because you don't deserve to have him in anymore of your projects. But we are giving you a chance to stop us from  boycotting your Studio and all your other projects from now by PUBLICLY APOLOGISING TO JOHNNY DEPP! We won't stand with you  if you stand with the abusers !
